## ΏθΠΩΎ╕Π Project Architecture

```text
AI-Math-Solver/
έΦΓ
έΦεέΦΑέΦΑ app.py
έΦεέΦΑέΦΑ gemini_server.py
έΦεέΦΑέΦΑ requirements.txt
έΦεέΦΑέΦΑ .gitignore
έΦΓ
έΦεέΦΑέΦΑ templates/
έΦΓ   έΦΦέΦΑέΦΑ index.html
έΦΓ
έΦεέΦΑέΦΑ static/
έΦΓ   έΦεέΦΑέΦΑ script.js
έΦΓ   έΦΦέΦΑέΦΑ style.css
έΦΓ
έΦΦέΦΑέΦΑ README.md
```

`app.py` handles the main Flask application, API routes, application state, drawing logic, and computer-vision pipeline.

`gemini_server.py` handles communication with the Gemini AI service.

The frontend communicates with the backend through API endpoints to provide an interactive solving experience.

