## ΏθΟχ Input Modes

| Mode | Description |
|---|---|
| έεΠΎ╕Π Mouse Draw | Draw mathematical equations directly on the canvas |
| ΏθΨΡΎ╕Π Hand Gesture | Draw in real time using hand tracking and a webcam |
| ΏθΨ╝Ύ╕Π Upload Image | Upload screenshots or photos of mathematical problems |
| έΝρΎ╕Π Type Equation | Enter mathematical expressions directly |

---

## ΏθΦΡ Security

Sensitive information such as API keys is stored using environment variables.

The following files/directories should remain excluded from Git:

```text
.env
.venv/
venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.log
```

Never expose API keys directly inside source code.

---

## ΏθΝΡ Deployment

Deployment support is planned using **Hugging Face Spaces**.

> **Note:** The local hand-gesture implementation uses webcam access and may require browser-side camera handling when deployed to a remote server. Server-side `cv2.VideoCapture(0)` cannot directly access a visitor's webcam.

The deployed architecture will therefore require special handling for the real-time gesture feature.

